ian.com/us-news/2025/j&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;an/26/trump-resumes-sending-2000-pound-bombs-to-israel-undoing-biden-pause&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">113895711051776775</guid><pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 16:57:10 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Carl Zimmer</title><link>https://mastodon.social/@Carl_Zimmer/113895982838924622</link><description>My new book AIR-BORNE comes out February 25. Scientific American calls it "astonishing." You can pre-order it here: &lt;a href="https://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/724793/air-borne-by-carl-zimmer/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://www.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;penguinrandomhouse.com/books/7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;24793/air-borne-by-carl-zimmer/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="https://files.mastodon.social/media_attachments/files/113/895/976/680/815/318/original/a70c506c47ebed1c.mp4"&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.mastodon.social/media_attachments/files/113/895/976/680/815/318/original/a70c506c47ebed1c.mp4" alt="Mastodon video" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">113895982838924622</guid><pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 18:06:17 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Daph la_réponse_D</title><link>https://oc.todon.fr/@daph/113896664175843933</link><description>Je suis tellement triste d’avoir loupé Lucie, l’intelligence artificielle de l’éducation nationale tellement pétée  qu’elle est pas capable de faire un calcul simple niveau CE2, qui a duré quatre jours et qui a dû être fermée. Lucie était prévue pour remplacer les profs absents.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/113/896/664/512/828/330/original/2e22c321b26f4aef.jpeg"&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/113/896/664/512/828/330/original/2e22c321b26f4aef.jpeg" alt="Mastodon image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">113899434786996756</guid><pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 08:44:09 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Konrad Kording</title><link>https://neuromatch.social/@kordinglab/113901988332296613</link><description>Announcing a new week-long program for young computational neuroscience/ behavior professors to talk about rigorous science, mentoring, lab management, and networking in a stunning retreat setting. Do great science as a community and have fun doing so.As assistant professors in neural, computational and behavioral science, it was hard to learn how to do good science, mentor students, navigate administration, while having fun. New 1 week academy for young professors: join us August 23-30, 2025 in Kingston, ON, Canada.Learn more and apply here: &lt;a href="https://lnkd.in/ecaatvc8" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=""&gt;lnkd.in/ecaatvc8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Great lecturers for key skills: Hannah Bayer, Patrick Mineault, Yael Niv, Megan Peters, and your hosts Gunnar Blohm and Konrad Kording, and of course networking with an amazing group of 30 other professors.</description><guid isPermaLink="false">113901988494085411</guid><pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 19:33:33 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Anne Applebaum</title><link>https://journa.host/@anneapplebaum/113902458421691517</link><description>American social media companies write the algorithms that determine what voters read; moderation systems are opaque; political advertising cannot always be tracked. Do European democracies, or any democracies, really have sovereign elections anymore?&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2025/03/musk-tech-oligarch-european-election-influence/681453/?gift=hVZeG3M9DnxL4CekrWGK3zd9JdZYQ1qXmZ-Tzbyq_Go&amp;amp;utm_source=copy-link&amp;amp;utm_medium=social&amp;amp;utm_campaign=share" rel="nofollow noopener" targe